30c2ae05ceea214dcc96fb1fd2ab.mp4?t=1769421567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can walk around cities, look out the window and watch the changes in nature, weather and architecture, listen to the radio and communicate with passengers. You can see forests, fields, mountains, cities and villages.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757610/extras/9730fd8467e874cef2ea9d2d7123d965.poster.avif?t=1769421567\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757610/extras/9730fd8467e874cef2ea9d2d7123d965.webm?t=1769421567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757610/extras/9730fd8467e874cef2ea9d2d7123d965.mp4?t=1769421567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game offers you an exciting journey through Russia by train, full of adventures, discoveries and emotions.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757610/extras/b1352ee512884b72d8d87ec71ce7a64f.poster.avif?t=1769421567\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757610/extras/b1352ee512884b72d8d87ec71ce7a64f.webm?t=1769421567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757610/extras/b1352ee512884b72d8d87ec71ce7a64f.mp4?t=1769421567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
